    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! It has been pampered and kept in truly pristine shape\u2014not a scratch or smudge in sight. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel that's so hard to find. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
