      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. The S54B32 straight-six remains the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned VANOS system that delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example features a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains remarkably stiff with zero bushing deflection, riding on an unmolested factory suspension setup. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the interior shows no bolster wear or pixel degradation in the instrument cluster. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
