    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a deep, mirror-like paint finish completely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom aroma; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and every tactile surface feels brand new. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched alloy wheels, this car offers a 'time capsule' experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection. It drives as tight and responsive as the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
